      <title>伊朗最高领袖：袭击以色列的导弹数量“小问题”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/iran-s-supreme-leader-number-of-missiles-that-hit-israel-trivial-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领导人赞扬了该国一周前对以色列的报复性打击，尽管他认为德黑兰打击目标的成功率低是一件微不足道的事情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/iran-s-supreme-leader-number-of-missiles-that-hit-israel-trivial-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
