    <item>
      <title>美国众议院通过950亿美元援助乌克兰、以色列和台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六通过了对乌克兰 610 亿美元的新援助，结束了长达六个月的政治僵局，在此期间基辅的库存因与俄罗斯的战争而减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
